The aim of the group is to share not only general experiences about life as a (Lusophone) immigrant in the Netherlands, but also to give useful information and (when possible, expert) advice in the following topics:

- Preparing to migrate to the Netherlands
- Work and Education
- Housing
- Family Reunification
- Civic Integration Exams
- Undocumented Migration
- Learning Dutch
- Learning Portuguese
- Business, Finance and Taxes
- Government and Public Policy
- Tourism, Shopping and Leisure
- Maternity and Family
- Relevant events for the Lusophone community

The group is private and has now over 6.000 members. Membership requests are carefully screened to prevent spam and fake profiles. 

https://www.facebook.com/groups/vivendonaholanda'}]
